cc:Work.dc:title: A Desirable Future in Image Processing and Analysis
cc:Work.dc:description: The combination of different softwares should be simplified (in the near future). Using **KNIME** to create workflow that integrates the machine learning capabilities of **Ilastik**, followed by further processing and analysis in **ImageJ/FIJI** and finally leveraging **R** for data analysis and representation.
